SECTION 8. OTHER EVENTS
Item 8.01 Other Events
On January 23, 2007, Buckeye Technologies Inc. (the Company) received notice from NYSE Regulation, Inc. (NYSE) that it was deficient in meeting the requirements of the following section of the New York Stock Exchange Listed Company Manual:
303A.12(a) Failed to make disclosure regarding NYSE CEO certification in annual report to shareholders.
The Company is filing this Form 8-K in order to cure this disclosure deficiency.
The Chief Executive Officers annual certification regarding NYSEs corporate governance listing standards was submitted to the NYSE on November 30, 2005. The Company failed to include this disclosure in the Companys 2006 annual report to shareholders, as required by Section 303A.12(a). The Company will include the disclosure required by Section 303A.12(a) in its 2007 annual report to shareholders.
 
 
 
