COOPERATION; SUBROGATION
 
11.
 
  All agreements and obligations of the Company contained in this Agreement shall continue during the period Indemnitee is a Director or Officer and shall continue thereafter, even though Indemnitee may have terminated his or her service as a Director or Officer of the Company, so long as Indemnitee shall be subject to any threatened, pending or completed Proceeding by reason of Indemnitees Corporate Status.
