This SECOND AMENDED AND RESTATED CREDIT AGREEMENT () is entered into as of October 22, 2010 among BUCKEYE TECHNOLOGIES INC., a Delaware corporation (the ), certain Subsidiaries of the Company from time to time party hereto as guarantors (collectively, the  and individually, a ), each lender from time to time party hereto (collectively, the  and individually, a ), and BANK OF AMERICA, N.A., as Administrative Agent, Swing Line Lender and L/C Issuer.
