(d)           any redemption, retirement or other repurchase obligation of the Company, any of its Subsidiaries or any other Loan Party under any Organization Document, agreement, instrument, deed or lease.
No approval, authorization or other action by, or declaration to or filing with, any governmental or administrative authority or any other Person is required to be obtained or made by the Company, any of its Subsidiaries or any other Loan Party in connection with the execution, delivery and performance of this Agreement, the Notes or any other Loan Document, the transactions contemplated hereby or thereby, the making of any borrowing hereunder or the guaranteeing of the Obligations or the securing of the Obligations with the Collateral (other than filings necessary to perfect the Administrative Agents security interest in the Collateral).
