6.15          .  Neither the Company nor any of its Subsidiaries shall enter into any agreement, instrument, deed or lease which prohibits or limits the ability of the Company or any of its Subsidiaries to create, incur, assume or suffer to exist any Lien upon any of their respective properties, assets or revenues, whether now owned or hereafter acquired or which requires the grant of any collateral for such obligation if collateral is granted for another obligation, except the following:
