The Company will from time to time cause any Subsidiary (other than (x) an Immaterial Subsidiary or (y) a Foreign Subsidiary that does not constitute a Material Foreign Subsidiary) within 30 days (provided that, in the case of a Foreign Subsidiary, the Company shall be permitted such additional time as may be reasonably necessary to effectuate the purposes of this Section 10.09 provided the Company is diligently pursuing the same) after any such Person (a) in the case of a Domestic Subsidiary, ceases to be an Immaterial Subsidiary or (b) in the case of a Foreign Subsidiary, becomes a Material Foreign Subsidiary (or, to the extent applicable under clauses (a)(ii) or (b)(ii) of the definition of Material Foreign Subsidiary, is designated to become a Guarantor), to join this Agreement as a
 
