are adjusted operating income,
adjusted net income, adjusted earnings per share, free cash flow and are equal to net income, pre-tax income, operating income and earnings per share excluding the after-tax effects of alternative fuel mixture credits (AFMC) and cellulosic biofuel credits (CBC), goodwill and long-term asset impairment cost, and
restructuring cost.
