8.4 . For purposes of this Agreement, the term:
Certain Definitions
"" means a confidentiality and standstill agreement that contains confidentiality and standstill provisions that are no less favorable in the aggregate to the Company than those contained in the Confidentiality Agreement; , , such confidentiality agreement shall not be required to prohibit the making or amendment of a non-public Competing Proposal to the Company Board.
