The address of the registered office Buckeye Technologies Inc. (the "") in the State of Delaware shall be at 1209 Orange Street, Wilmington, Delaware 19801. The Corporation may have other offices, both within and without the State of Delaware, as the board of directors of the Corporation (the "") from time to time shall determine or the business of the Corporation may require.
